N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 246.14 - Severability

State Regulations

Each section, or portion thereof, of this Part shall be
deemed severable, and in the event that any section, or portion thereof, of
this Part is held to be invalid, the remainder of this Part shall continue in
full force and effect. Notes
